Anti Terrorist Rush 2 - Gameplay Trailer (iOS - Android)

Join to our shootout. The bandits have captured a military base and are waiting for retribution from you. Upgrade your hero, look for new weapons and equipment. All items, pistols, body armor are combined with each other to form more powerful copies. Find all collection of items and beat the terrorists. Special weapons will help your hero. Have a good game!

App Store iOS Download link:

Google Play Android Download link:
